{"tid":510502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★狂賀！減慢 iPhone 事件--Apple已面臨至少兩宗集體訴訟。","createTime":"2017-12-26T14:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T04:40:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"145e2b71aa1716c0851c1662b8f5ecd1e0d9912e","tid":510502,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:17:54.000Z","msg":"雖然 Apple 在確認此事時講明減慢舊 iPhone 速度是為了避免老化的電池不勝負荷而突然關機，但是市場上有不少聲音指 Apple 事前保持「低調」，目的是要讓用戶以為手機開始故障、繼而購入新型號的 iPhone；而為此，<span style=\"color: red;\">Apple 正面臨至少兩起來自集體訴訟</span>。<br />\n<br />\n根據提出訴訟的其中一個律師代表指出，Apple 在不告知用戶的前提下私自減慢 iPhone 的運行速度，是蓄意的違法行為；而另一邊、位於加洲的原訴方亦表示，Apple 理應讓用戶自行選擇是否減慢速度。<br />\n<br />\n訴訟目前仍未有結果，如果最後真是罪名成立，Apple 將有可能<span style=\"color: red;\">需要為受影響的用戶提供賠償</span>，更重要的，是 Apple 往後將不能透過同樣手段讓用戶自動自覺地購入新機，或者會影響到未來新 iPhone 的銷量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=16185\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Fnews2.php%3Fid%3D16185&d=aQNfnfxYN1hGCgQEnulAvUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b4cb0389\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ringhk.com/news2.php?id=16185</a>"},{"pid":"4fe174244511e9ba80ecb4d83a2eb9b2c02c8cb5","tid":510502,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69700b829b82f27da8acc7df879ef5073a399f28","tid":510502,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T14:18:54.000Z","msg":"需要為受影響的用戶提供賠償<br />\n需要為受影響的用戶提供賠償<br />\n需要為受影響的用戶提供賠償<br />\n需要為受影響的用戶提供賠償<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/1